Definition: a day on which work is suspended by law or custom
Example: no mail is delivered on federal holidays; it's a good thing that New Year's was a holiday because everyone had a hangover
Synonyms: day, a, on, which, work, is, suspended, by, law, or, custom, no, mail, delivered, federal, holidays, it, s, good, thing, that, New, Year, was, because, everyone, had, hangover
Category: noun.time
